value.name: SCMS-T: Content Protection and 4 Things You Need to Know
value.snippet: CSR Harmony’s SCMS-T method is only compatible with devices that use SCMS-T copy protection. If you are using a device like a headset or any other audio device without the SCMS support, you will not be able to connect or stream the content. In many cases, the SCMS is disabled by default from the company, resulting in connectivity issues.
